<%= @tournament.name %>
===============================================

Hi <%= @user.username %>.

A new tournament was added to the SSB Tournament Manager.

Name: <%= @tournament.name %>
Date: <%= @tournament.date.to_s(:custom_datetime_with_weekday) %>
Registration fee: <%= @tournament.registration_fee %> CHF
Location:
<%- @tournament.location.split(',').each do |str| %>
  <%= str.strip %>
<%- end %>

To join this tournament, just follow the link and click the green button:
  <%= @url %>

We wish you good luck during your matches!
